listing_name: 3 in 1 Wireless Charging Station, Fast Wireless Charger Stand for iPhone 15/14/13/12 X Pro Max & Apple Watch,[Foldable & Double Coil] Compatible with Apple Watch Ultra 8/7/6/5 Airpods 2/3/Pro
special_features: Lightweight Design, Short Circuit Protection, Charging Indicator, Wireless Charging
about_this_item:
[CHARGE INSTANTLY] Joyroom wireless charger stand has built-in dual coils. In traditional induction, you have to have sort of perfectly matched coils. They must be very close to each other and they have to be in perfect alignment. But with two coils, you don't need that. Just toss our phone on the charging pad to charge instantly.
[3 IN 1] Our 3-in-1 charging station takes up a bank card space and can easily charge smartphones, earphones with wireless charging, and Apple Watch at once by only using one cord. Wireless charger stand compatible with iPhone 15/ 14 Pro Max/14 Pro/14 Plus/14/13 Pro Max/13 Pro /13 /12 Pro Max/12 Pro/12/11 Pro Max/11 Pro/11/XS/XS Max /XS/XR/X/8 Plus/8ã€iWatch Series 8/7/6/5/4/3/2/1/SEã€AirPod pro 2/Pro/3/2 and models of Samsung Galaxy, Google, LG, etc
[Foldable and Compact Design] The phone charging station can be folded into a mobile phone size for easy portability, and the slim design of only 0.6lb weight makes it easy to fit into a backpack or luggage. In the past, you'd have to unplug all your home chargers and carry an entire charging station and multiple cords before traveling, but this 3-in-1 charger can eliminate all that for you. One plug and done!
[Heat Dissipation Technolgy] This phone charging station is certified by FCC, CE, ROHS, and UL. With 262 heat-dissipation holes on the back of the charging pad and an inner heat-dissipation unit make sure your phone is at the optimum temperature to provide the Max charging speed. Not only does this product easily manage your device batteries, but it also charges them at an adequate rate
[What You Will Get] Package includes 1x Wireless Charger Stand; 1x USB Type-C Cable(3.3 feet); 1x 18W QC 3.0 Charger Adapter; 1x User Manual
[Purchase Instructions] All wireless charging speeds are slower than charging with a cable. After the phone is charged to 80%, it will enter trickle charging mode to reduce the charging speed and extend the life of the phone battery. The thinner the phone case, the faster the charging speed. The Apple Watch Ultra has the largest battery capacity, so it takes 3-6 hours to fill, and the charging speed is determined by the ambient temperature. It is best to use the original AirPods, non-original AirPods without temperature protection may damage the headphones

about_this_item:
Baseus Car charger Particular Digital Display QC+PPS Dual Quick Charger Car Charger 65W - Silver
With a Baseus charger, you will get rid of the problem of one input and the limitation of charging only one device. With the super-strong charger, you can charge your laptop and phone at the same time at the USB-C input: 45 W and USB input: 18 W.
The BSP II intelligent charging technology is able to automatically adjust voltage, current, and power management. The charger has a dual-port, one for USB and one for USB-C. When using the PD port alone, it is able to charge at 65W, while using only the USB port, it is able to charge at 30W. When using both inputs, the power is divided into PD: 45W and USB: 18W respectively, giving a total of 63W.
Devices with an older interface charge approximately 20% of the battery in 30 minutes, while a Baseus device can charge up to 60% of the battery at the same time. This allows you to use applications such as navigation and noticeably charge your phone at the same time.
The charger does not overheat despite charging 2 devices at once. It is compatible with different phones, but when the battery level of the devices being charged reaches 100%, it automatically stops charging them, thus extending their life significantly.

about_this_item:
High Capacity 10000mAh: The Joyroom JR-L016 Power Bank boasts a substantial 10000mAh capacity, providing ample power to charge your devices multiple times. This high capacity makes it an ideal companion for travel, outdoor activities, or as a reliable backup power source.
Dual Ports (USB & PD): Featuring both a standard USB port and a Power Delivery (PD) port, this power bank allows simultaneous charging of two devices. The PD port supports fast charging for compatible devices, ensuring quick and efficient power delivery.
Built-In Multi-Cable Design: The JR-L016 is equipped with a built-in cable design, featuring Lightning, Type-C, and Micro USB connectors. This all-in-one cable design eliminates the need for additional cables, offering convenient charging for a variety of devices.
37W Output: With a high output of 37W, this power bank ensures rapid charging for your devices. The robust power output caters to the power requirements of modern smartphones, tablets, and other gadgets, providing a quick and reliable charge.
Built-In Flashlight: The inclusion of a built-in flashlight adds an extra layer of functionality to the power bank. This feature comes in handy during outdoor activities, emergencies, or when you simply need additional illumination in low-light situations.

Das GerÃ¤t bietet ein kleines Display, um aktuelle Daten abzulesen. Ãœber einen Knopf lÃ¤sst sich der Ladestrom am GerÃ¤t selbst einstellen. Optional kann das Ladekabel auch Ã¼ber eine App angesteuert werden, um den Ladevorgang z.B. verzÃ¶gert zu starten oder dort die Ladeleistung zu Ã¤ndern.

Die 7m LÃ¤nge des Kabels sind super, so kommt man an die meisten Autos ran.

Praktisch aber hÃ¤sslich: die Halterung fÃ¼r das LadegerÃ¤t. Diese lÃ¤sst sich super an die Wand schrauben und passt perfekt. Leider ist das Bild darauf wirklich Geschmackssache - etwas neutraleres wÃ¤re besser.

Der Preis ist meines Erachtens nach im Vergleich zur Konkurrenz deutlich zu hoch.', 'Este cargador lo que hace es agilizar los tiempos de carga y hacernos la vida mÃ¡s fÃ¡cil para no estar pendientes de la carga eligiendo el tramo horario que mÃ¡s nos beneficia para conseguir un ahorro importante. AdemÃ¡s no te complicas con instalaciones avanzadas, lo enchufas en casa y listo, carga tu coche rapidito con hasta 7,6 kW de potencia.

El diseÃ±o es chulo, blanco con un Ã¡guila que le da un toque muy proamericano y el cable es larguÃ­simo, 7 metros.

La app es muy buena, porque controlas todo desde el mÃ³vil. Pones cuÃ¡ndo quieres que cargue el coche y te ahorras unos euros con la tarifa de noche. AdemÃ¡s, estÃ¡ hecho siguiendo las normas de seguridad alemanas, que ya sabes que ellos en esto de la calidad se lo curran.

En casa carga el triple de rÃ¡pido que los puntos de carga de la calle y, aunque solo vale para dentro, Â¿para quÃ© quieres mÃ¡s rollos si en tu garaje ya estÃ¡s apaÃ±ado?

En fin, estÃ¡ bastante bien porque te quita dolores de cabeza. Es verdad que el precio puede hacer que te lo pienses dos veces, pero como dicen, lo bueno se paga y, sinceramente, te da esa tranquilidad de que estÃ¡s invirtiendo en algo que no te va a fallar.', 'Ich habe bereits eine Wallbox testen dÃ¼rfen, nur leider durfte diese laut Elektriker nicht in Deutschland betrieben werden.

So habe ich mehr Hoffnung in das mobile LadegerÃ¤t von Tera gehabt.
Geliefert wurde es in einer praktischen Tasche, was praktisch fÃ¼r den Transport ist.

Im Innerden der Tasche war das LadegerÃ¤t mit einem sehr langem Ladekabel, einer Wandhalterung inkl. Montagematerial und einer Anleitung und ein CE-Zertifikat, was schon mal ein gutes Zeichen war.
Die Verarbeitung und QualitÃ¤t sind super und viel besser als erwartet.

Das Display ist gut abzulesen und so auch ohne App Einsatzbereit.
Dank Touch Display benÃ¶tigt man nicht viele KnÃ¶pfe auf der â€Steuereinheitâ€œ selbst.
Mit der App hat man jedoch viel mehr MÃ¶glichkeiten, was die Informationen und Protokollierung angeht.

Mit einer CEE Steckdose bei 240V und bis zu 32 Ampere, konnte mir der Elektriker problemlos eine Dose unter das Carport anbringen.
Mit dem Typ 2 Stecker kann man dann viele gÃ¤ngige E-Autos/Hybriden laden.
Von Tesla, Audi, BMW, Hyundai usw. werden solche Stecker verbaut.

Ich bin super zufrieden mit dem Produkt, auch wenn ich mich nicht so gut damit auskenne.
